snippet.title: The Machines Arena - Alpha Teaser
snippet.description:
https://www.themachinesarena.com/
The Machines Arena is a 4v4 top-down hero shooter. Every match is a short and intense multiplayer showdown where players team up against other players to fight for victory.

Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/p6a97bKZ6H

Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/themachinesgame 
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/themachinesgame
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/themachinesgame
